21:21.405 --> 21:24.284
I don't want tough.
I want nice.

21:24.366 --> 21:25.618
I want gentle.

21:25.701 --> 21:26.702
Oh.

21:28.370 --> 21:30.043
I want you.

21:31.874 --> 21:34.593
