have those in there.

22:33.018 --> 22:34.986
Barry thought it would be a...

22:36.647 --> 22:39.400
...a laugh in a...
in a stressful situation.

22:39.483 --> 22:44.239
I said at the time,
that's not a good idea.

22:44.321 --> 22:46.449
Give those back.
I don't know why somebody...

22:46.615 --> 22:47.992
(CRINKLING SOUNDS)

22:48.200 --> 22:51.500
That's completely...
inappropriate.

22:51.704 --> 22:52.921
(RATTLING SOUNDS)

22:57.293 --> 23:00.172
Good job, brah.
That's it for today.

23:00.254 --> 23:01.597
Today?

23:01.672 --> 23:03.845
- I have to do more of this?
- It'll get easier.

23:03.924 --> 23:05.801
You gotta remember what
you're doing is a good thing.

23:05.885 --> 23:07.478
It's horrible.

23:07.553 --> 23:09.021
But...

23:10.055 --> 23:12.934
...it's fulfilling.
(SIGHS)

23:17.271 --> 23:19.490
(STOMACH GROWLS)

23:20.733 --> 23:24.283
<i>TIP: Hi, Duncan, it's Dr. Tip calling
from the Center for Fertility.</i>

23:24.361 --> 23:27.865
<i>Look, I'm gonna level with you,
you've got a smoking hot wife,</i>

23:27.948 --> 23:29.666
<i>and you're moping around
with a wet noodle.</i>

23:29.742 --> 23:32.621
<i>If you don't get her pregnant
soon, somebody else will.</i>

23:32.703 --> 23:35.206
<i>- Come on.
- Be a man and ask for help.</i>

23:35.289 --> 23:36.586
<i>Call me.</i>

23:36.665 --> 23:38.963
How is this guy a doctor?

23:39.627 --> 23:42.756
All right.
Let's, uh...

23:42.838 --> 23:44.966
...let's see here.

23:46.759 --> 23:48.636
There you go.

23:48.719 --> 23:52.815
So far... so good.

23:53.807 --> 23:55.275
(SLOSHING SOUNDS)

23:56.518 --> 23:58.486
Uh... no.
That's strange.

23:58.562 --> 24:01.532
I'm in the right...
Hold on.

24:02.399 --> 24:03.742
(DOCTOR GRUNTS)

24:04.234 --> 24:07.488
Huh-huh-huh-huh-huh.
Where are you?

24:08.280 --> 24:10.157
Yula, can you hold the
chart up for me?

24:11.283 --> 24:14.253
Huh, that is strange.
I'm right in the right spot,

24:14.328 --> 24:15.875
and there's no polyp in here.

24:15.955 --> 24:18.253
I'm right there.
I'm right in the neighborhood.

24:18.749 --> 24:20.126
I'm knocking...

24:21.126 --> 24:23.629
...but no one's home.

24:23.712 --> 24:25.589
- Jesus!
(GROWLING)

24:25.673 --> 24:27.971
(SCREAMING)
(MUFFLED SCREAMING)

24:37.559 --> 24:39.402
What the fuck?

24:44.400 --> 24:46.653
(SNORING)

24:50.239 --> 24:52.867
I-I-I honestly,
I didn't know where else to go.

24:52.950 --> 24:54.748
I mean, it was just
a weird night.

24:54.827 --> 24:56.500
I mean,
I had this horrible dream.

24:56.578 --> 24:59.752
And the guy I work with
was killed by a rabid raccoon.

24:59.832 --> 25:01.505
- What?
- And then the night before,

25:01.583 --> 25:03.176
I woke up in the bathroom.

25:03.252 --> 25:05.380
I woke up in the bathroom,
and I didn't know what happened.

25:05.462 --> 25:06.930
What do you want me to do?

25:07.881 --> 25:09.849
I want you to hypnotize me.

25:12.761 --> 25:14.513
Fantastic.

25:15.514 --> 25:20.065
In your own time,
please tell me...

25:20.394 --> 25:21.486
...what you see.

25:23.605 --> 25:25.983
I'm standing in front
of an office building.

25:26.608 --> 25:28.406
It's where I work.

25:28.485 --> 25:31.455
Can you tell me about your work?

25:31.530 --> 25:35.580
It's a financial services company.
It's not very fulfilling.

25:35.659 --> 25:39.584
Lately, it's been stressful.
Very...

25:39.663 --> 25:41.882
(STOMACH GROWLS)
- Very stressful.

25:41.957 --> 25:43.425
Are you alone?

25:43.500 --> 25:46.800
No. I'm with my mother.

25:46.879 --> 25:48.597
And where is your father?

25:49.131 --> 25:51.225
My father's not there.

25:52.509 --> 25:53.601
Why?

25:54.386 --> 25:57.435
My parents divorced
when I was eight.

25:57.514 --> 25:59.232
(BIRD SQUAWKING)
Abandonment issues.

25:59.308 --> 26:01.231
- Shut up!
- Abandonment issues.

26:01.310 --> 26:04.610
- I'll clip your wings.
(DUNCAN'S STOMACH GROWLS)

26:06.148 --> 26:07.400
Go on.

26:11.987 --> 26:13.660
Sarah?

26:13.739 --> 26:15.662
And Sarah's there?

26:15.741 --> 26:18.665
She's right over there.

26:18.744 --> 26:20.462
On the grass.

26:20.537 --> 26:22.289
And what does Sarah want?

26:22.372 --> 26:26.218
I know what she wants.
She wants a family.

26:26.293 --> 26:28.091
- And I just don't know if I...
(STOMACH GROWLS)

26:28.170 --> 26:31.640
...if I'll ever be a good...
good dad.

26:31.715 --> 26:35.310
I know, I know, I know
it will make you happy.

26:36.095 --> 26:39.975
But I don't... I just want to wait
to have a kid.

26:40.057 --> 26:42.776
My mother hired
this asshole fertility doctor.

26:42.851 --> 26:44.353
(GROWLING)
- Oh, my God!

26:44.436 --> 26:46.029
(SHOUTS)

26:46.105 --> 26:47.357
(STOMACH GROWLING LOUDLY)

26:47.439 --> 26:49.908
(DUNCAN SCREAMS AND MOANS)

26:53.987 --> 26:55.989
(SCREAMS)

26:57.199 --> 27:00.078
(SCREAMS, MATERIAL RIPS)

27:00.202 --> 27:01.203
Wow.

27:10.504 --> 27:13.007
(RIPPING)

27:15.551 --> 27:17.349
(GRUNTS)

27:27.354 --> 27:28.446
(EXCLAIMS)

27:29.731 --> 27:32.826
Hey-hey-hey!
Just hold it right there.

27:32.943 --> 27:35.492
Stay right there.
Stay right there, you hear me?

27:35.612 --> 27:37.080
(GROWLS)
- Whoa!

27:37.156 --> 27:39.909
- No! No! No! No!
(GROWLING)

27:40.993 --> 27:42.370
(MUTTERING)

27:42.452 --> 27:44.170
Mr. Hayslip.

27:44.246 --> 27:46.340
I'm going to count
from three down to one.

27:46.415 --> 27:49.214
And when I reach one,
you're gonna wake up.

27:49.293 --> 27:50.419
Do you understand?

27:50.502 --> 27:52.300
Three, two...

27:52.379 --> 27:54.598
(SCREAMING)

27:54.673 --> 27:56.266
Get off!

27:56.341 --> 27:57.388
One!

28:03.515 --> 28:05.563
(BOTH SCREAMING)

28:07.644 --> 28:09.362
(SHOUTING) What is that?!

28:11.815 --> 28:13.317
(SCREAMING)

28:13.400 --> 28:14.993
(SQUAWKING)

28:16.737 --> 28:18.330
(ALL STOP SCREAMING)

28:20.657 --> 28:22.705
(GRUMBLING)

28:32.252 --> 28:34.050
(CAR ALARM BLARES)
- He's gone.

28:34.796 --> 28:36.890
It just went out the window.

28:36.965 --> 28:39.093
(ALARMS BLARE)

28:43.180 --> 28:44.432
Wow.

28:45.641 --> 28:47.439
How's your ass?

28:48.268 --> 28:49.690
(BREATHES HEAVILY)

28:56.318 --> 28:58.036
This might help.

29:00.781 --> 29:02.078
And this.

29:04.368 --> 29:07.463
I should've spotted it
when you first walked in.

29:07.537 --> 29:09.585
- My life is over.
- It's in the eyes.

29:09.665 --> 29:12.043
Always in the eyes.
Sorry.

29:12.125 --> 29:14.253
What the fuck are
you talking about?

29:14.336 --> 29:16.839
It's not in the eyes.
That thing came out of my ass.

29:16.922 --> 29:18.845
- It was ins...
- Shh.

29:18.924 --> 29:20.050
What do we do?

29:20.133 --> 29:21.601
Just wait. Wait.

29:21.677 --> 29:24.271
Wait, what?
For what?

29:24.346 --> 29:27.441
For somebody to snap
their fingers and wake me up?

29:27.516 --> 29:30.144
Cause my life is over.
Did I mention that my life is over?

29:30.227 --> 29:33.481
I'm gonna just go home to my wife.
And... Oh, my God, Sarah.

29:33.563 --> 29:36.658
Hey, Sarah, I'm home. Guess what?
I have an alien in my ass.

29:36.733 --> 29:41.239
There is this ancient myth

29:41.321 --> 29:45.542
surrounding the anus.

29:46.785 --> 29:49.629
Here it is. Look at this.

29:51.373 --> 29:54.798
The myth of our anus.

29:55.168 --> 30:00.049
You see, before religion became
the primary focus of our society,

30:00.132 --> 30:03.306
there was a beautiful time
where mythology

30:03.385 --> 30:06.389
and legends filled our beings.

30:06.888 --> 30:08.390
What does this have
to do with me?

30:08.473 --> 30:12.478
Listen, I believe
that this very same creature

30:12.561 --> 30:14.609
came out of your anus

30:14.896 --> 30:18.150
and attacked your co-worker.

30:18.900 --> 30:20.902
- Alistair?
- Precisely.

30:21.278 --> 30:24.657
When you're pushed into a corner
by someone,

30:24.740 --> 30:28.165
this creature comes out
and attacks that someone.

30:28.243 --> 30:30.337
In this case, it was me.
Look here.

30:30.412 --> 30:32.585
My ass, I got bitten.
(LAUGHS)

30:33.165 --> 30:35.259
What if I have more
inside of me?

30:35.584 --> 30:38.963
Well, if that's the case,
we have to kill this thing.

30:39.046 --> 30:40.719
No, no, no.
You're missing the point.

30:40.797 --> 30:43.175
This thing is a part of you.

30:43.258 --> 30:45.477
Don't you understand?
It's your subconscious.

30:45.886 --> 30:47.138
It's your raw desires.

30:47.220 --> 30:49.894
No, I didn't mean to hurt Alistair.
I don't want to hurt anybody.

30:49.973 --> 30:51.975
(MAKING APE SOUNDS)

30:52.309 --> 30:55.939
We're still apes, Hayslip.
Don't you understand?

30:56.021 --> 31:00.026
Maybe you didn't want
to hurt him in here.

31:00.108 --> 31:02.702
But I think you wanted
to hurt him in here.

31:03.070 --> 31:04.913
And in here.

31:06.865 --> 31:10.961
If you kill it, you're gonna kill
a very important part of yourself.

31:11.036 --> 31:13.334
You see,
that fear, worry and anger

31:13.413 --> 31:16.212
are essential to the
human beings

31:16.291 --> 31:21.172
as long as we can control them
and use them to our advantage.

31:21.254 --> 31:22.801
My mentor always told me,

31:23.256 --> 31:25.509
"Stop carrying the horse
on your shoulders.

31:25.592 --> 31:27.594
Put him between your legs,
and ride him!"

31:29.137 --> 31:31.139
What are you...
What are you talking about?

31:31.515 --> 31:32.858
It's a metaphor.

31:33.517 --> 31:35.986
I had a monster up my ass!

31:36.061 --> 31:38.109
This is the furthest thing
from a metaphor!

31:38.188 --> 31:40.156
Listen! if you kill it,

31:40.232 --> 31:43.156
it would be just like
giving yourself a lobotomy.

31:43.235 --> 31:45.704
You would become a zombie.
Not a good idea.

31:46.363 --> 31:51.745
This creature is a physical
manifestation of your dark side.

31:51.827 --> 31:55.172
- What?
- You gotta accept this.

31:55.247 --> 31:57.591
Accept it.
Take it to yourself.

31:58.333 --> 31:59.676
Bond with it.

31:59.751 --> 32:02.254
That's your only way
to control it.

32:02.337 --> 32:05.056
But listen to me,
the most important thing now,

32:05.132 --> 32:07.635
when it returns,
and it will return,

32:07.717 --> 32:10.220
(MUTTERS)
- It will try to get

32:10.303 --> 32:12.852
- back inside of you.
- What? What?

32:12.931 --> 32:13.932
- What?
- Yeah.

32:14.015 --> 32:16.894
It will try to get inside of you.

32:16.977 --> 32:19.321
- No. No.
- Of course.

32:19.396 --> 32:22.741
Before it does,
you have to bond with it.

32:24.609 --> 32:25.701
Okay?

32:26.278 --> 32:27.996
All right, let me
get this straight.

32:28.071 --> 32:31.075
- Hmm?
- You want me to bond with it?

32:33.076 --> 32:37.627
And if I do, you're saying
there's a very good chance

32:37.706 --> 32:39.458
that it won't hurt anybody else?

32:40.333 --> 32:42.836
Hopefully.
(CHUCKLES, SNORTS)

32:46.047 --> 32:48.095
So now what?

32:49.968 --> 32:51.641
We wait.

33:04.983 --> 33:06.405
<i>WOMAN: Oh, my God.</i>

33:06.485 --> 33:09.739
Oh, God.
Oh... Oh, God.

33:09.821 --> 33:12.324
(MOANING)

33:15.452 --> 33:17.329
Oh.

33:17.412 --> 33:19.665
Oh, God.

33:19.748 --> 33:21.876
(LAUGHS)

33:21.958 --> 33:24.006
Oh, wow.

33:24.419 --> 33:27.263
They teach you that
in medical school?

33:27.756 --> 33:30.384
- Sort of.
- Hmm.

33:30.467 --> 33:32.970
So, uh, my turn now?

33:33.053 --> 33:35.147
Oh. I don't do that.

33:37.057 --> 33:38.525
You're being serious?

33:38.600 --> 33:42.275
Yes. But you got my number.
So call me.

33:46.316 --> 33:48.318
(SIGHING)

33:48.401 --> 33:50.449
All right, Larry.

33:50.529 --> 33:53.453
It's just us out here.

33:53.532 --> 33:55.034
Here we go.

33:55.116 --> 33:56.834
Focus.

33:58.954 --> 34:00.206
(EXHALES)

34:01.414 --> 34:03.007
(GLASS BREAKS, CAT HISSES)

34:03.375 --> 34:04.592
Brittany?

34:04.793 --> 34:06.636
Change your mind?

34:09.130 --> 34:11.804
(CRASHING)

34:15.971 --> 34:17.768
Hello?

34:17.847 --> 34:20.690
Brittany?
Don't be a little bitch.

34:20.766 --> 34:22.690
(SCREAMS)

34:29.067 --> 34:30.819
(LAUGHING)

34:36.283 --> 34:39.286
(HARMONICA PLAYS)

34:54.384 --> 34:57.433
(DEMON HUMMING)

35:08.148 --> 35:09.650
Oh, no.

35:09.983 --> 35:11.576
Hayslip! Hayslip.

35:11.985 --> 35:15.114
Hayslip. Wake up.
Wake up. Wake up!

35:15.196 --> 35:16.698
Hey! Hey!

35:16.781 --> 35:17.748
- What?
- There.

35:18.366 --> 35:21.961
